1255 POST STREET

SAN FRANCISCO, CALIFORNIA 94109
410171-1149
May 11, 1972
Dear Nugget Prospect:
On behalf of the entire
San Francisco 49er organization,
we thank you for your interest in wanting to become
a 1972
Niner Nugget.
The Nuggets have become an integral part of the 49er promo-
tional program.
are proud of the reputation
established by
the group and look forward to twenty of
you to carry on and
expand upon that reputation.
A 1972 Niner Nugget will have the opportunity to take
part in a number of promotional activities between now and the
start of the season,
to see and take part in each of the 4yer
home games during the season, and to help keep "49er Fever"
during the off-season.
Specifically,
all judging WiLL DE
completed by May 15th, and you will be notified by mail shortly
thereafter as to whether or not you have been selected.
The first meeting of the group will be on Thursaay, June 1st.
At that time, you will be given the Niner Nugget outfit.
The
group will also begin singing rehearsals that evening.
There
will be various shopping center promotions during June and
July, golf tournaments, and hospita
promotions in June,
July
Many other activities will be discussed at
future
meetings.
The group will sing at all 49er home games and will
have opportunities to take part in many booster club banquets
and 49er related functions during the months of September, October,
November and December.
Please be your-
Good Luck!
Dick Berg
Director of Promotions
